 Znači, u to vrijeme

456
00:17:23,440 --> 00:17:25,560
 je bila vrlo teška nam situacija,

457
00:17:25,560 --> 00:17:27,080
 jer smo, ja i troje djeca,

458
00:17:27,080 --> 00:17:28,280
 živjeli u Dalmaciji,

459
00:17:28,280 --> 00:17:30,720
 a oni i najstariji sin

460
00:17:30,720 --> 00:17:32,160
 koji je tada bio školarac,

461
00:17:32,160 --> 00:17:33,280
 su živjeli u Zagrebu,

462
00:17:33,280 --> 00:17:35,440
 u garsonjeri njegovog brata,

463
00:17:35,440 --> 00:17:37,500
 ili su živjeli u toj nedovršenoj kući

464
00:17:37,500 --> 00:17:38,520
 bez struje vode.

465
00:17:38,520 --> 00:17:40,840
 To je bila vrlo teška situacija

466
00:17:40,840 --> 00:17:41,940
 gdje smo mi, naravno,

467
00:17:41,940 --> 00:17:43,980
 htjeli napokon opet živjeti zajedno

468
00:17:43,980 --> 00:17:45,440
 kao obitelj,

469
00:17:45,440 --> 00:17:47,440
 međutim, nismo imali šahtove,

470
00:17:47,440 --> 00:17:49,260
 nismo imali vodu,

471
00:17:49,260 --> 00:17:50,380
 nismo imali struju.

472
00:17:50,380 --> 00:17:52,360
 To znači da nemaš ni tigrije.

473
00:17:52,360 --> 00:17:54,500
 Oni su tamo svokotali.

474
00:17:54,500 --> 00:17:56,500
 Mislim, to je bilo hrabro od njih i tada,

475
00:17:56,500 --> 00:18:00,940
 ali cilj nam je bio opet biti zajedno.

476
00:18:00,940 --> 00:18:03,700
 I onda nastupa naša draga gospa

477
00:18:03,700 --> 00:18:05,380
 gdje smo mi rekli ovako,

478
00:18:05,440 --> 00:18:07,080
 nema majstora, mi ne znamo

479
00:18:07,080 --> 00:18:08,220
 kako se ovo može riješiti.

480
00:18:08,220 --> 00:18:12,220
 I kažem ja svom sinu

481
00:18:12,220 --> 00:18:13,760
 koji je jedini tada bio sa mnom u Zagrebu,

482
00:18:13,760 --> 00:18:15,600
 ajmo mi gospi negdje na hodačašće

483
00:18:15,600 --> 00:18:16,280
 pa ćemo vidjeti.

484
00:18:16,280 --> 00:18:18,940
 I ja sjetim da ima jedna kapela na sljemenu,

485
00:18:18,940 --> 00:18:20,780
 idemo mi jednu nedilju lijepo na sljeme,

486
00:18:20,780 --> 00:18:22,640
 dolje to će biti naši hodačašće,

487
00:18:22,640 --> 00:18:24,420
 dragoj gospi, siguro će se nešto dogoditi.

488
00:18:24,420 --> 00:18:26,140
 Mi tako odemo,

489
00:18:26,140 --> 00:18:28,240
 ponedljak u jutro, 7 sati,

490
00:18:28,240 --> 00:18:30,160
 zove mene jedan majstor od ovih

491
00:18:30,160 --> 00:18:31,120
 koji smo zvali.

492
00:18:31,880 --> 00:18:33,260
 E, znaš šta, ja sam dobio kuću

493
00:18:33,260 --> 00:18:35,280
 za izgradnju 500 metara od vaše,

494
00:18:35,280 --> 00:18:36,640
 mogu napraviti vaš šaht.

495
00:18:36,640 --> 00:18:38,800
 I čovjek samo dođe i napravi ga.

496
00:18:38,800 --> 00:18:40,120
 Eto, to je samo jedan primjer

497
00:18:40,120 --> 00:18:41,080
 kako gospa pomaže.

498
00:18:41,080 --> 00:18:43,200
 I onda još samo trebalo spojiti,

499
00:18:43,200 --> 00:18:45,400
 a eto, grad Zagreb nije nikako se odaziva,

500
00:18:45,400 --> 00:18:46,380
 opet par mjeseci,

501
00:18:46,380 --> 00:18:47,940
 i onda mi kažemo,

502
00:18:47,940 --> 00:18:49,880
 evo sveti Jospe, mi ćemo...

503
00:18:49,880 --> 00:18:50,580
 Čekaj, čekaj.

504
00:18:50,580 --> 00:18:52,740
 Da.

505
00:18:52,740 --> 00:18:54,960
 Za laufao se.

506
00:18:54,960 --> 00:18:55,620
 Da.

507
00:18:55,620 --> 00:18:58,100
 Pao.

508
00:18:58,100 --> 00:18:59,620
 Hvala.

509
00:18:59,620 --> 00:19:10,460
 Uglavnom, naši nama su dolazili oni u Dalmaciju,

510
00:19:10,460 --> 00:19:12,880
 Krešo i naš najstariji sin,

511
00:19:12,880 --> 00:19:15,640
 i sin se jednu nedelju užasno rasplakao,

512
00:19:15,640 --> 00:19:17,060
 nije više ti joj ići u Zagreb,

513
00:19:17,060 --> 00:19:18,160
 nije ti joj ići u školu.

514
00:19:18,820 --> 00:19:21,980
 Ja sam vidjela da tu mi više nemamo svoje snage,

515
00:19:21,980 --> 00:19:23,880
 kako će mi natjerat grad, vodovod,

516
00:19:23,880 --> 00:19:25,420
 da nam dovede vodu u tu kuću.

517
00:19:25,420 --> 00:19:29,000
 I dok su se oni vozili,

518
00:19:29,000 --> 00:19:30,340
 ja mu govorim, znaš šta, Krešo,

519
00:19:30,340 --> 00:19:32,720
 nema nam druge, moramo moliti.

520
00:19:32,720 --> 00:19:35,400
 Molit ćemo, evo ovog čovjeka tu,

521
00:19:35,400 --> 00:19:36,140
 prijatelja,

522
00:19:36,140 --> 00:19:38,520
 vama s desne, s lijeve,

523
00:19:38,520 --> 00:19:39,320
 na slici,

524
00:19:39,320 --> 00:19:41,860
 zaštitnika, obitelji,

525
00:19:41,860 --> 00:19:44,600
 očeva, inženjera,

526
00:19:44,600 --> 00:19:45,940
 djece, trudnica,

527
00:19:47,760 --> 00:19:49,580
 najboljega zapitanja,

528
00:19:49,580 --> 00:19:52,140
 zapitanja, rješavanja stambenog pitanja.

529
00:19:52,140 --> 00:19:55,300
 I onda smo odlučili moliti 30-odnevnicu

530
00:19:55,300 --> 00:19:56,280
 Svetom Josipom

531
00:19:56,280 --> 00:19:59,360
 i za vrijeme te 30-odnevnice,

532
00:19:59,360 --> 00:20:00,500
 točnije, ono ne znam,

533
00:20:00,500 --> 00:20:01,600
 taj zadnji tjedan,

534
00:20:01,600 --> 00:20:03,240
 sam se ja jako razboljila,

535
00:20:03,240 --> 00:20:04,220
 došla je ta korona,

536
00:20:04,220 --> 00:20:04,920
 nesretna,

537
00:20:04,920 --> 00:20:06,260
 ono, sa troje djece

538
00:20:06,260 --> 00:20:08,000
 i malom bebom koje sam i dojela.

539
00:20:08,000 --> 00:20:09,960
 U to vrijeme sam se razboljila

540
00:20:09,960 --> 00:20:12,460
 do te mjere da nisam mogla ništa,

541
00:20:12,460 --> 00:20:13,580
 nisam mogla dignuti žlicu,

542
00:20:13,580 --> 00:20:14,780
 roditelji su me hranili.

543
00:20:14,780 --> 00:20:17,880
 I to je tako sve u tom trenutku,

544
00:20:17,880 --> 00:20:21,140
 znači sve izgledalo kao da se naš život raspada,

545
00:20:21,140 --> 00:20:23,560
 ne, da ćemo mi biti opet zajedno

546
00:20:23,560 --> 00:20:25,240
 ili živjeti u našoj kući zajedno,

547
00:20:25,240 --> 00:20:28,100
 svi djeca su bila tužna

548
00:20:28,100 --> 00:20:28,680
 i tako,

549
00:20:28,680 --> 00:20:31,660
 to je baš izgledalo grozno,

550
00:20:31,660 --> 00:20:34,820
 koda je nekakva tragedija na pomolu,

551
00:20:34,820 --> 00:20:36,260
 ali ne nešto dobro.

552
00:20:36,260 --> 00:20:40,720
 I bio je sveti Nikola,

553
00:20:40,720 --> 00:20:43,460
 to je bio zadnji dan zapravo 30. dnevnice,

554
00:20:43,460 --> 00:20:45,040
 ja sam ono, to izmolula,

555
00:20:45,040 --> 00:20:48,660
 iako nisam pet dana spavala od te korone,

556
00:20:48,660 --> 00:20:50,940
 izmolula sam nekako,

557
00:20:50,940 --> 00:20:53,020
 nemam pojma na koji način,

558
00:20:53,020 --> 00:20:55,400
 čula sam se s njim na večer,

559
00:20:55,400 --> 00:20:57,220
 on je umirivo sina

560
00:20:57,220 --> 00:20:59,200
 i evo, on može sad još.

561
00:20:59,200 --> 00:21:01,400
 I onda smo mi izmolili,

562
00:21:01,400 --> 00:21:02,340
 ja i on u Zagrebu,

563
00:21:02,340 --> 00:21:04,940
 zadnju večer tu u 30. dnevnicu,

564
00:21:04,940 --> 00:21:06,840
 i onako sam baš iz srca rekao,

565
00:21:06,840 --> 00:21:07,480
 sveto mi Jospe,

566
00:21:07,480 --> 00:21:08,320
 evo, sveti Jospe,

567
00:21:08,320 --> 00:21:09,080
 ako ne radi mene,

568
00:21:09,080 --> 00:21:09,900
 radi ovog djeteta,

569
00:21:09,900 --> 00:21:11,380
 samo radi ovog djeteta,

570
00:21:11,380 --> 00:21:12,380
 pokaži da možeš.

571
00:21:12,380 --> 00:21:15,140
 I otišli smo spavali,

572
00:21:15,140 --> 00:21:17,080
 ujutro 7 sati,

573
00:21:17,080 --> 00:21:18,660
 opet zoni mobita.

574
00:21:18,660 --> 00:21:20,360
 Reko, daj me nemoj,

575
00:21:20,360 --> 00:21:21,080
 ko je sad?

576
00:21:21,080 --> 00:21:24,160
 Ej, mi smo došli iz grada Zagreba,

577
00:21:24,160 --> 00:21:24,980
 di je ta voda,

578
00:21:24,980 --> 00:21:25,740
 di treba spojiti,

579
00:21:25,740 --> 00:21:26,620
 što treba spojiti?

580
00:21:27,220 --> 00:21:27,840
 Dragom Bogu,

581
00:21:27,840 --> 00:21:28,960
 to je nevjerojatno.

582
00:21:28,960 --> 00:21:30,340
 Svetom Josipu, hvala.

583
00:21:30,340 --> 00:21:32,360
 Koliko smo samo u tim trenutcima

584
00:21:32,360 --> 00:21:33,640
 osjećali njihovu potporu.

585
00:21:33,640 --> 00:21:35,840
 I svoji mi sad završili

586
00:21:35,840 --> 00:21:38,460
 kako je Bog rješio naše probleme

587
00:21:38,460 --> 00:21:40,440
 i kako je Bog nas doveo

588
00:21:40,440 --> 00:21:41,460
 do mjesta gdje ne se želo.

589
00:21:41,460 --> 00:21:42,940
 Mi smo sad presretni u toj kući.

590
00:21:42,940 --> 00:21:44,960
 A šta je tu ključno bilo po meni?

591
00:21:44,960 --> 00:21:46,340
 Bog je od uvijek znao

592
00:21:46,340 --> 00:21:47,740
 da ćemo imati puno djece,

593
00:21:47,740 --> 00:21:49,340
 gdje ih treba smjestiti.

594
00:21:50,020 --> 00:21:51,360
 I dao nam je posao

595
00:21:51,360 --> 00:21:52,440
 da radimo od doma,

596
00:21:52,440 --> 00:21:54,320
 da imamo vremena za njih,

597
00:21:54,320 --> 00:21:55,840
 da su mama i tata uvijek doma,

598
00:21:55,840 --> 00:21:57,180
 da uvijek može biti skuhano,

599
00:21:57,180 --> 00:21:58,360
 da uvijek može biti opravano,

600
00:21:58,360 --> 00:21:59,460
 da uvijek nas mogu zagrli,

601
00:21:59,460 --> 00:22:01,880
 da ju uvijek možemo dočekati.

602
00:22:01,880 --> 00:22:03,960
 I to je onaj način koji smo vam htjeli reći

603
00:22:03,960 --> 00:22:05,140
 kako je Bogu sve moguće,

604
00:22:05,140 --> 00:22:06,200
 čak i u današnje vrijeme.

605
00:22:06,680 --> 00:22:07,900
 Nemojte se bojati ničega.

606
00:22:07,900 --> 00:22:09,440
 Sigurno sve može,

607
00:22:09,440 --> 00:22:10,840
 samo se utječite dragom Bogu.

608
00:22:10,840 --> 00:22:12,000
 To je sto posto tako.

609
00:22:12,000 --> 00:22:12,940
 Evo, to vam i možemo

610
00:22:12,940 --> 00:22:14,400
 i našeg primjera posljedočiti.

611
00:22:14,400 --> 00:22:16,240
 Evo, i sad još samo,

612
00:22:16,240 --> 00:22:18,460
 evo, pošto je tema ljubav,

613
00:22:18,460 --> 00:22:20,800
 možda bi o tome mogli nešto reći.

614
00:22:20,800 --> 00:22:21,680
 Evo ćeš ti prva.

615
00:22:21,680 --> 00:22:24,520
 Mi kad smo razmišljali o toj temi ljubavi,

616
00:22:24,520 --> 00:22:25,700
 mislili smo, pa dobro,

617
00:22:25,700 --> 00:22:28,480
 šta nećemo sad nas dvoje tu stati i govoriti,

618
00:22:28,480 --> 00:22:29,680
 pa dobro, ja njega volim,

619
00:22:29,680 --> 00:22:30,380
 on mene voli.

620
00:22:30,380 --> 00:22:32,180
 Mislim, to je valjda jasno

621
00:22:32,180 --> 00:22:34,380
 s obzirom na broj djece.

622
00:22:34,380 --> 00:22:41,460
 Ali mislim, stvarno ono u braku,

623
00:22:41,460 --> 00:22:43,940
 i što je Frad Stjepan govorio u propovjedi,

624
00:22:43,940 --> 00:22:45,560
 nema bez žrtve.

625
00:22:45,560 --> 00:22:47,900
 To je tajna ljubav.

626
00:22:47,900 --> 00:22:50,380
 To stvarno, moraš se odreći samog sebe,

627
00:22:50,380 --> 00:22:52,800
 zaista, svega svoga i ambicije,

628
00:22:52,800 --> 00:22:55,420
 i svega, i muškarci, i žene.

629
00:22:55,420 --> 00:22:56,700
 Žedama je možda lakše,

630
00:22:56,700 --> 00:22:58,580
 jer one su inkubator,

631
00:22:58,580 --> 00:23:00,900
 kad si trudna, jednostavno se totalno

632
00:23:00,900 --> 00:23:04,480
 prepustiš čuvanju tog djeteta,

633
00:23:04,480 --> 00:23:06,560
 i nekako prirodno ti dođe

634
00:23:06,560 --> 00:23:08,580
 da se odrekneš svega.

635
00:23:08,580 --> 00:23:10,280
 Ali muškarcima je to teže još.

636
00:23:10,280 --> 00:23:12,700
 Ali, vjerujte mi, isplaci se.

637
00:23:12,700 --> 00:23:14,860
 I koliko će vas žena voljeti više

638
00:23:14,860 --> 00:23:17,060
 kad vidi da ju vi podupirete,

639
00:23:17,060 --> 00:23:21,760
 da ne sjedite vani sa dečkima na pivi,

640
00:23:21,760 --> 00:23:23,200
 nego da ste doma sa njom,

641
00:23:23,200 --> 00:23:25,180
 ili da ju pomažete oko djeteta.

642
00:23:25,180 --> 00:23:28,060
 Vjerujte, bit ćete radosni cijeli život

643
00:23:28,060 --> 00:23:28,980
 dečki s time.

644
00:23:29,620 --> 00:23:32,520
 Ali razmišljali smo o tome

645
00:23:32,520 --> 00:23:33,640
 što je nama bila ljubav,

646
00:23:33,640 --> 00:23:35,540
 i onda nam je samo došlo više

647
00:23:35,540 --> 00:23:38,700
 kako smo mi kroz naš život

648
00:23:38,700 --> 00:23:41,820
 i to dobivanje djece i svega

649
00:23:41,820 --> 00:23:43,920
 osjećali od drugih ljudi ljubav.

650
00:23:43,920 --> 00:23:47,080
 A to je jedna velika zajednica,

651
00:23:47,080 --> 00:23:48,680
 veća zajednica,

652
00:23:48,680 --> 00:23:50,920
 kroz sve te teškoće koje smo mi prolazili,

653
00:23:50,920 --> 00:23:52,400
 nama je obitelj naša bila

654
00:23:52,400 --> 00:23:55,300
 jako sklonao.

655
00:23:55,300 --> 00:23:59,240
 I sad, kad pitam sama sebe što je to ljubav,

656
00:23:59,240 --> 00:24:00,720
 kad sam ja osjetila ljubav,

657
00:24:00,720 --> 00:24:02,880
 a po meni su to tako,

658
00:24:02,880 --> 00:24:06,500
 ono, to možda stvari koje iskipaćamo zdravo zagotovo,

659
00:24:06,500 --> 00:24:08,240
 ali koje su,

660
00:24:08,240 --> 00:24:10,680
 koje ti stvarno daju snago.

661
00:24:10,680 --> 00:24:12,400
 Kad ti, na primjer,

662
00:24:12,400 --> 00:24:14,660
 kad ti sve krova pošalje lona carne

663
00:24:14,660 --> 00:24:16,160
 ili ne znam, galon raštike,

664
00:24:16,160 --> 00:24:19,080
 kad ti mama bolesna,

665
00:24:19,080 --> 00:24:20,440
 ima isto koronu,

666
00:24:20,440 --> 00:24:21,920
 ali diže se iz kreveta i kaže,

667
00:24:21,920 --> 00:24:24,320
 gle, ja ću sad čuvat tebe i tvoje troje djece.

668
00:24:24,320 --> 00:24:25,120
 Ja je kažem, mama,

669
00:24:25,120 --> 00:24:26,800
 ajde u kreveć, šta ti je?

670
00:24:26,800 --> 00:24:28,320
 Ti imaš 70 godina,

671
00:24:28,320 --> 00:24:29,620
 ja ne imam toliko.

672
00:24:29,620 --> 00:24:32,720
 Ne želim ono da umreš.

673
00:24:32,720 --> 00:24:34,460
 Ona govori, pa šta je meni,

674
00:24:34,460 --> 00:24:36,500
 šta sam ja sebi bitna?

675
00:24:36,500 --> 00:24:39,160
 Pa bitnija si mi ti i tvoja djeca od mene sami.

676
00:24:40,680 --> 00:24:43,340
 Pa onda kad ti did ko ima 70 godina

677
00:24:43,340 --> 00:24:45,640
 sjedne u Dalmaciji u auto,

678
00:24:45,640 --> 00:24:46,860
 vozi tri sata

679
00:24:46,860 --> 00:24:48,620
 da ti doveze auto,

680
00:24:48,620 --> 00:24:50,000
 jer zna da se tvoj pokvario

681
00:24:50,000 --> 00:24:51,920
 i da ne možeš razvazati djecu

682
00:24:51,920 --> 00:24:52,880
 u školu vrtičnom,

683
00:24:52,880 --> 00:24:53,820
 tisuću obaveza.

684
00:24:53,820 --> 00:24:56,960
 Znači, sjedne u auto čovjek

685
00:24:56,960 --> 00:24:59,320
 i doveze ti auto u 70 godina.

686
00:24:59,320 --> 00:25:01,780
 Kad ti svetstra dođe iz Zadra,

687
00:25:01,780 --> 00:25:03,620
 vas sedam u kući,

688
00:25:03,620 --> 00:25:05,000
 povraća i ima koronu

689
00:25:05,000 --> 00:25:05,660
 ili ne znam šta,

690
00:25:05,660 --> 00:25:09,160
 ona dođe i kuhat za tebe,

691
00:25:09,320 --> 00:25:10,720
 tvoju djecu, čuva djecu.

692
00:25:10,720 --> 00:25:12,120
 Kad, ne znam,

693
00:25:12,120 --> 00:25:13,900
 neoženjeni stric,

694
00:25:13,900 --> 00:25:15,900
 uzmeti tvoje troje djece,

695
00:25:15,900 --> 00:25:17,600
 znači ne znam ni pelenu presuć

696
00:25:17,600 --> 00:25:19,680
 i dovedeti ih u Zagrebi,

697
00:25:19,680 --> 00:25:20,360
 zimutskog.

698
00:25:20,360 --> 00:25:21,500
 Znači,

699
00:25:21,500 --> 00:25:23,260
 to su neke,

700
00:25:23,260 --> 00:25:24,820
 to su situacije,

701
00:25:24,820 --> 00:25:25,400
 ili recimo,

702
00:25:25,400 --> 00:25:26,660
 kad nam je bilo najteže,

703
00:25:26,660 --> 00:25:27,780
 kad smo oboje bili

704
00:25:27,780 --> 00:25:29,160
 bolestni,

705
00:25:29,160 --> 00:25:30,600
 a bilo je i takvih situacija,

706
00:25:30,600 --> 00:25:33,180
 imali smo jednu dadilju,

707
00:25:33,280 --> 00:25:34,980
 ona se pretvorila u hobotnicu.

708
00:25:34,980 --> 00:25:35,640
 Znači,

709
00:25:35,640 --> 00:25:36,140
 pere,

710
00:25:36,140 --> 00:25:36,660
 kuha,

711
00:25:36,660 --> 00:25:37,900
 nabavlja namirnice,

712
00:25:37,900 --> 00:25:39,640
 djecu tušira,

713
00:25:39,640 --> 00:25:41,820
 meni pere kosu

714
00:25:41,820 --> 00:25:42,640
 i tako dalje.

715
00:25:42,640 --> 00:25:45,580
 To su sve te neke situacije

716
00:25:45,580 --> 00:25:47,580
 u kojem ti osjetiš

717
00:25:47,580 --> 00:25:49,060
 ono da si voljen

718
00:25:49,060 --> 00:25:51,080
 i to ti je zapravo ljubav.

719
00:25:51,080 --> 00:25:51,320
 Evo,

720
00:25:51,320 --> 00:25:53,180
 to što ja osjećam da je ljubava,

721
00:25:53,180 --> 00:25:53,680
 to je ono

722
00:25:53,680 --> 00:25:56,380
 kad Sveti Pavao govori

723
00:25:56,380 --> 00:25:58,380
 što je ljubav ili što nije

724
00:25:58,380 --> 00:25:59,640
 i kad kaže

725
00:25:59,640 --> 00:26:01,580
 a meni najviše uvijek ono ostane

726
00:26:01,580 --> 00:26:04,540
 ne traži svoje.

727
00:26:04,540 --> 00:26:06,600
 Znači,

728
00:26:06,600 --> 00:26:08,760
 svi ti ljudi koji su nama pomagali,

729
00:26:08,760 --> 00:26:11,220
 oni su se sebe odrekli

730
00:26:11,220 --> 00:26:12,840
 da nama to vrijeme daju

731
00:26:12,840 --> 00:26:14,680
 i da nama pomognu

732
00:26:14,680 --> 00:26:16,040
 kad mi nismo mogli sami.

733
00:26:16,040 --> 00:26:18,920
 A Bog ti uvijek tako i šalje ljude

734
00:26:18,920 --> 00:26:20,800
 i mame i tate i djedove

735
00:26:20,800 --> 00:26:22,740
 i stričeve i sestre

736
00:26:22,740 --> 00:26:24,880
 i ne poznate ljude

737
00:26:24,880 --> 00:26:26,780
 da te podrže

738
00:26:26,780 --> 00:26:28,940
 i mi kad smo i mislili

739
00:26:28,940 --> 00:26:30,180
 da nam je najteže

740
00:26:30,180 --> 00:26:31,740
 da naša obitelj će propasti

741
00:26:31,740 --> 00:26:32,480
 i raspasti se,

742
00:26:32,480 --> 00:26:34,760
 nikad se to na kraju nije dogodilo.

743
00:26:34,760 --> 00:26:35,920
 Evo, tu stojimo pred vama,

744
00:26:35,920 --> 00:26:38,880
 živi, zdravi, radosni

745
00:26:38,880 --> 00:26:41,760
 i...

746
00:26:41,760 --> 00:26:44,200
 I da čekamo se vrati svoji djeci.

747
00:26:44,360 --> 00:26:46,240
 Eto, hvala vam, evo, hvala vam

748
00:26:46,240 --> 00:26:47,640
 što ste nas postišali i to...

749
00:26:47,640 --> 00:26:51,460
 Hvala što pratite kanal.

